Neotoma Dataset 2905

Venyukovka-1 Exposure pollen dataset

DOI: doi:10.5072/FK22R3TS97

Links: View on Neotoma Explorer | Raw JSON

Constituent Database: Pollen Database of Siberia and the Russian Far East

Dataset Type: pollen

Latitude: 47.1167

Longitude: 138.583

Age Range: 4700 - 7400 ybp

Description: Floodplain terrace of river. Physiography: river valley. Surrounding vegetation: meadow, bog and floodplain forest.
